sources.description:
A Worrisome Thing - A euthanasia doctor, his wife, and son are befriended by seemingly innocent neighbors who plot the family's murder to appease radical religious opposition to assisted suicide.
2022.  Stars: Amelia Yokel, Kailen Duffield, Chad Yenney
